        public void conversationAPI(java.lang.String input,
                            com.ibm.watson.developer_cloud.conversation.v1.model.Context context,
                            java.lang.String workspaceId)
        Takes in the user Input and sends it to IBM Watson API. If IBM Watson API understands the intent, it would return the appropriate response. Else, the chatbot would print the default response.
        Parameters:
        input - User's input chat message
        context - Context of activity
        workspaceId - IBM Watson API key
